{"tid":905408,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸十年毒奶","createTime":"2018-11-17T05:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T03:59:11.000Z","uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69c6e3a7b1f2abe55f76db78f30391fc0635d233","tid":905408,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/785120835162374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F785120835162374%2F&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=a0318dae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/785120835162374/</a><br />\n<br />\n《毒奶十年‧傷未癒》<br />\n【結石寶寶十年病纏身】<br />\n【家長維權千日未了願】<br />\n<br />\n十年前，三聚氰胺毒奶粉風暴吹散京奧圓滿閉幕的喜悅，將國人拖進人人自危的惶恐深淵。事件改變無數家庭命運，近三十萬嬰幼兒受害。<br />\n<br />\n有線中國組先後走訪了多位當年三聚氰胺毒奶粉受害者，受影響的內蒙古奶農，以及遠赴新西蘭，探訪當地奶農，奶企和中國代購商，製作一連三集的特輯《毒奶十年》。<br />\n<br />\n十年過去，後患仍然纏繞不少受害者。<br />\n<br />\n當年大部分受影響幼兒的家長，都選擇接受二千至數萬元不等的賠償，息事寧人。只有個別父母堅持討回公道，甚至為此身陷牢獄，付出沉重代價。<br />\n<br />\n第一集《傷未癒》探討他們的心路歷程。<br />\n<br />\n第一集(上)《傷未癒》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/785120835162374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F785120835162374%2F&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=a0318dae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/785120835162374/</a><br />\n<br />\n第一集(下)《代購潮》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/353637198736876/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F353637198736876%2F&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=0f72a0b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/353637198736876/</a><br />\n<br />\n#毒奶十年<br />\n#結石寶寶<br />\n#趙連海<br />\n#2018年11月9日節目重温<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"80f5e9d047bbf9f423f5da0a2ef403b20c01b222","tid":905408,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1941878575956619/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1941878575956619%2F&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=72973653\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1941878575956619/</a><br />\n<br />\n《毒奶十年‧擴張》<br />\n【中國奶企大舉進軍海外投資奶粉廠】<br />\n【需求令當地乳業欣欣向榮】<br />\n<br />\n毒奶事件後，除了中國本土乳業面臨重整，不少涉及三聚氰胺事件的奶企也大舉進軍海外，包括到乳業大國新西蘭併購奶廠和牧場，再將產品反銷中國，欲重奪被外國品牌佔據的奶粉市場。<br />\n<br />\n中國對外國奶粉的需求，也推動新西蘭的乳業急促發展。2008年後，新西蘭奶價飆升，當地的農場亦不斷擴張。<br />\n<br />\n但這條依靠外國奶源、供應國內奶業的生產之路，是否可持續呢?<br />\n<br />\n第一集(上)《傷未癒》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/785120835162374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F785120835162374%2F&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=a0318dae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/785120835162374/</a><br />\n<br />\n第一集(下)《代購潮》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/353637198736876/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F353637198736876%2F&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=0f72a0b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/353637198736876/</a><br />\n<br />\n第二集(上)《蕭條》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1941870985957378/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1941870985957378%2F&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=f5a37772\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1941870985957378/</a><br />\n<br />\n第二集(下)《擴張》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1941878575956619/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1941878575956619%2F&d=VfQSqtYW%2FR06Q5t0YvuTU%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=72973653\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1941878575956619/</a><br />\n<br />\n#毒奶十年<br />\n#嬰兒配方奶粉<br />\n#信心危機<br />\n#madeinNewZealand<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"de9144780cbd208cb4826dcb50b8b0ce4f861f43","tid":905408,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"有線算講得好客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345bbae9b24e4e8ebfa900df52fffb00797aa4ef","tid":905408,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:06:54.000Z","msg":"治癒心靈系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83200cd23f991ad4468beda5f6ab9eaad5c1b122","tid":905408,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41b642bf41b91af919c10e96abed369ea03d87e","tid":905408,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"來生不做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e945c03221eabcaa76828ccc603f4a4e0f68fb8e","tid":905408,"uid":62842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"講到口臭，中國得假野係真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbddedbf871fb92cec9ed72c5c64ed4a27e2f7a","tid":905408,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"552398ab576488997dce04d774efec91c959242b","tid":905408,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"好了蒼疤忘了痛<img sr